{"tid":884097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢中mma】屯門58M乘客疑因排隊爭執　兩男激鬥三分鐘","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T12:11:22.000Z","uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"48593b11773523e030bb0ab4c54178d939b79b79","tid":884097,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"網上流傳片段，指今（31日）早上約9時45分於良景邨巴士站一輛58Ｍ雙層巴士內，兩名中年男乘客懷疑因排隊問題爭執，繼而動武。全段片長共長3分鐘10秒，片內可見一名藍衣男與一名橙衣男首先在近車門位置互相動手，其後移入車廂內繼續打鬥。<br />\n<br />\n打架期間不斷對罵<br />\n<br />\n近半分鐘後，橙衣男將藍衣男壓倒在地上，抱起其雙腳作「倒豎葱」狀，藍衣男攤在地上，一度使出「撩陰腿」。片段中約一分鐘後，橙衣男攤在樓梯口，藍衣男躺在走廊位置，兩人雙腳互纏，互相指罵。其後橙衣男再踢藍衣男一下，藍衣男用手握住其腳部，橙衣男仍然踢他的上半身。兩人繼續對罵，並嘗試互脫對方鞋子。<br />\n<br />\n期間車長坐在車內司機位，旁觀者指有人已就事件報警，並講述：「一個話唔排隊吖嘛，咪打起上嚟囉。」<br />\n<br />\n警方證實，巴士司機於9時45分報案，指兩名男子在車上打架，兩輛救護車到場把兩人送往屯門醫院治理，案件列作「打鬥」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/253368/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4mma-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%8058m%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E6%BF%80%E9%AC%A5%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E9%90%98?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F253368%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4mma-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%258058m%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%259F%25B7-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%25BF%2580%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=FwYAA6jDIqA0QZLQKYkRCgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=484e3ed7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/253368/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4mma-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%8058m%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7-%E5%85%A9%E7%94%B7%E6%BF%80%E9%AC%A5%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E9%90%98?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打，往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8fc5e7c8f411aaf77f80970c338c60fbca34fa","tid":884097,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d7080d614b1c1630f9c32cfb3762e3de6ebbc7","tid":884097,"uid":31060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"屌啦星...<br />\n<br />\n拍片打橫呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc26bfc132bdeb75b4477486d65c63fdf956a12","tid":884097,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"屯門人啲質素係差啲"},{"pid":"a5533727797df166199dc64b9430f6960a0ecf29","tid":884097,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}